भाल्ल
Bhālla is the name or patronymic of a teacher who bears the<BR>patronymic Prātṛda in the Jaiminīya Upaniṣad Brāhmaṇa<BR>(iii. 31, 4).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=2-102&d=VEI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=vei&e=2262" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भाल्लवि
