Bhaima-sena, ‘descendant of Bhīmasena,’ is the name of<BR>a man in the Maitrāyaṇī Saṃhitā (iv. 6, 6).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=2-112&d=VEI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=vei&e=2297" target="_blank">Correction</a>

