Su-kurīra. See Kurīra.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=2-453&d=VEI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=vei&e=3588" target="_blank">Correction</a>

