Sutvan Kairiśi Bhārgāyaṇa is, in the Aitareya Brāhmaṇa<BR>(viii. 28, 18), the name of a king who, being taught a spell by<BR>Maitreya Kauṣārava, slew five kings and became great.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=2-453&d=VEI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=vei&e=3594" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सुदक्षिणक्षैमि
