सुदेवी
Su-devī. See Sudas.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=2-455&d=VEI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=vei&e=3602" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सुधन्वनाङ्गिरस
Su-dhanvan Āṅgirasa (‘descendant of Aṅgiras’) is the<BR>name of a teacher in the Bṛhadāraṇyaka Upaniṣad (iii. 3, 1).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=2-455&d=VEI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=vei&e=3603" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सुनीथशौचद्रथ
